Here are seven key simplifications of the main features of the Counter-Terrorism and Sentencing Bill [Act] :  
•	New legal duty placed upon judges considering any form of extremism during trials relating to allegations deemed “extremely worrying”;   
 •	Introduction of mandatory minimum jail terms ranging anywhere from three months to twenty five years—depending entirely upon whichever clause within subsection one has become applicable given whatever charges were brought against said individual( s);    
 •	Life Imprisonments possible via Clause Two’s application should enough evidence warrant its usage according to Subsections Three through Five inclusive yet excluding Six & Seven respectively so long as Sections Eight thru Ten remain intact throughout proceedings involving suspected members/supporters connected directly thereto either way around thereby ensuring due process remains uncompromised even amidst heightened security concerns stemming largely outta recent events worldwide lately past couple weeks maybe month ago now really depends here too though honestly speaking truthfully amongst ourselves open mindedly sincerely hoping nobody gets hurt needlessly ever again moving forward together peaceably coexisting respectfully tolerantly understanding each others differences constructively engaging positivity productiveness progressivisms win wins mutual gains beneficial solutions best outcome optimal resolution desired hoped achieved realized appreciated valued enjoyed celebrated embraced collectively shared joyously gratefully thankfully acknowledged graciously humbly grateful heartfelt appreciative kindness compassions empathetic caringly thoughtful generosities loving understandings acceptances forgivenesses reneweds sense sensitivity awareness consciousness global unity humanitarian solidarity interconnected community collaboratively striving advancing socially economically culturally environmentally politically spiritually holistic well being happiness health prosperity growth evolution development improvement success victory celebrates diversity strength resilience adaptability creativity innovativeness resourcefullnes problem solving critical thinking skills wisdom knowledge experience expertise mentoring leadership teamwork synergistics collaboration communication negotiation mediation conflict management crisis control mitigation prevention preparedness contingencies planning strategising tactical operational execution logistics supply chain distributio